    "description": "• PECIFICATIONS\n    • Voltage: AC 100V~240V/50~60Hz\n    • Power: 650W\n    • Fuse: 10A\n    • Ballast: 380V electronic ballast\n    • Lamp: OSRAM SIRIUS HRI 420WS\n    • Lamp Power: 420W\n    • Color temperature: 6800K ± 200K\n    • Lamp Life: 4000H\n    • Output lens diameter: 200MM\n    • Pan: 540° (16bit)\n    • Tilt: 270° (16bit)\n    • Beam angle: 1.2°\n    • Dimmer: 0-100% \n    • Strobe: 0-25Hz\n    • Color: CMY + 15 color\n    • Gobo: 17gobo + white light\n    • Prism: 8 prism, 8+8+8 honeycomb prisms (double prisms can be stacked to 32, and can rotate independently in both directions)\n    • Frost：10°Frost，soft and natural light spot\n    • Size: 372*312*631 (L*W*H)\n    • Channel: 24CH\n    • Control: DMX512, RDM,sACN\n    • Display: 1.8-inch color TFT screen on the display panel\n    • Intelligent control: Menu can record equipment usage time and light-on time, display channel data and software version information\n    • Error alarm: Automatic alarm for lamp failure\n    • Software upgrade: Upgrade files can be uploaded via DMX interface\n    • Appearance: Nylon high-temperature resistant plastic\n    • Lamp body color: Black\n    • Protection grade: IP55\n    • Cooling method: Air-cooled\n    • Net weight: 23kg",
